OL,7,FGrant Shapps is ordering a review of
OL,8,Fthe Ministry of Defence's diversity
OL,9,Fand inclusion policy following reports
OL,10,Fthat the Army wants to relax security
OL,11,Fchecks for overseas recruits to boost
OL,12,Fethnic minority representation.JThe
OL,13,Fdefence secretary said there will be
OL,14,Fno "lowering of security clearance
OL,15,Frequirements on my watch" after the
OL,16,FSunday Telegraph reported it had seen
OL,17,Fa British Army document vowing to
OL,18,F"challenge" security checks to
OL,19,Fincrease diversity.JThe newspaper said
OL,20,Fthe armed forces are looking overseas
OL,21,Fto attract ethnic minority talent
OL,22,Fbecause they have long failed to hit
OL,23,Frecruitment targets.JMr Shapps is said
OL,24,Fto be "genuinely furious about this
OL,25,Fwoke nonsense" and does not believe
OL,26,Fsuch policies are the way to address
