OL,7,F"We want people from all backgrounds
OL,8,Fto serve in our military but some
OL,9,Fpolicies appear to be more about a
OL,10,Fpolitical agenda than practically
OL,11,Fimproving the lives of our dedicated
OL,12,Fsoldiers and military personnel.
OL,13,F"There will certainly not be any
OL,14,Flowering of security clearance
OL,15,Frequirements on my watch. And no-one
OL,16,Fshould be offended by having religion
OL,17,Fas part of remembrance services.
OL,19,F"You don't have to be Christian to
OL,20,Fappreciate and respect the history and
OL,21,Ftraditions of the United Kingdom."
