OL,8,FSecretary said: "He's determined it is
OL,9,Frooted out on his watch. He's ready to
OL,10,Fgo to battle on it...
OL,12,F"There are personnel issues that need
OL,13,Faddressing in the armed services but
OL,14,Fsome of these policies are about a
OL,15,Fwoke agenda."JMeanwhile, fellow
OL,16,FCabinet minister Michael Gove said
OL,17,Fpolitical correctness should not
OL,18,F"impair our ability to defend our
