OL,7,FThe housing secretary told Sky's
OL,8,FSunday Morning with Trevor Phillips
OL,9,Fthat it is important to strike the
OL,10,F"right balance" to ensure the UK has a
OL,11,F"strong and diverse" military without
OL,12,Fletting "political correctness" and
OL,13,F"out there" approaches impairing the
OL,14,Fcountry's ability to "defend our
OL,15,Fborders".
