OL,7,F"Some of the policies that might apply
OL,8,Fappropriately in other workplaces
OL,9,Fwould not be appropriate in the
OL,10,Fmilitary," he added. An MoD spokesman
OL,11,Fsaid: "Our priority is protecting the
OL,12,Fnational security of the United
OL,13,FKingdom and ensuring the operational
OL,14,Feffectiveness of our armed forces.J"We
OL,15,Ftake security extremely seriously and
OL,16,Fensure that all personnel have the
OL,17,Fappropriate security clearance, which
OL,18,Fis reviewed on a case-by-case basis."
